data.description: Welcome and how about an assumable 4.99% VA Mortgage?  Come out before its gone!! This 1 yr new home is just waiting for you and comes with some great features! The low-density neighborhood is perfect for peace and quiet, including a horse farm across the street.  Not far from Eglin AFB, shopping and even the beach. Many upgrades include the large porcelain farm sink, upgraded granite in the kitchen and baths, pull down attic stairs, and an extra cement pad for the trash cans.  Take a look at the master bath with separate garden tub and an oversized tile shower.  Seller is leaving the high-end washer and dryer and the ADT alarm system, including exterior security cameras. Attic flooring added for easy storage above the garage.
